{"tid":594852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚耀宗: 強迫 ? 中國人必須唱國歌！ 會有專業執法部門處理","createTime":"2018-03-16T07:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T07:56:53.000Z","uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"92e5be4549b14d9ca1327c422b442dc84eceb46f","tid":594852,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:38:00.000Z","msg":"政府公布《國歌法》本地立法建議，列明公開及故意篡改和貶損國歌，即屬犯法，又建議中小學須教育學生唱國歌、了解國歌的歷史和精神，以及遵守國歌奏唱的禮儀。 正在北京出席人大會議的港區人大代表兼主席團成員譚耀宗認為，作為中國人必須懂得唱國歌，在學校從小開始學習，是合適的做法，不算強迫。 譚耀宗說，立法後除非有人想以身試法，否則不應用國歌作二次創作，認為可以選擇其他題材，與創作自由無關。 他認為，國歌法立法後，會對不尊重國歌的行為有阻嚇力，相信執法部門會有專業判斷如何處理。"},{"pid":"137f973adb1d4215772e2dee8d8759e0bcec9914","tid":594852,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39bf705187adfe04f39d327d6439db89ac8f75e0","tid":594852,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:44:53.000Z","msg":"專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10de18ccb168debb55172607b18659e5c6ab316f","tid":594852,"uid":22422,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:47:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">了解國歌的歷史和精神</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2017/01/Tianhan-350x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FTianhan-350x400.jpg&h=2893c94d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"619f18170d02be727d7e687a8b07c20e79f193b0","tid":594852,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:48:15.000Z","msg":"大家第日唔好唔聽話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比人捉架啦"},{"pid":"10eec19201f2d5cabd79e8a6c9c7545672a760b7","tid":594852,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0